  "body": "**What happened**:\r\n\r\ncurrently cloud-controller-manager use [`restclient.ServerAPIVersions()` ](https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/master/cmd/cloud-controller-manager/app/controllermanager.go#L263-L269) to wait for apiserver to be healthy.\r\nWe should deprecate or remove `ServerAPIVersions` and make use of `/healthz` as all other components do.\r\n\r\n\r\n**Environment**:\r\n- Kubernetes version (use `kubectl version`):\r\n- Cloud provider or hardware configuration:\r\n- OS (e.g. from /etc/os-release):\r\n- Kernel (e.g. `uname -a`):\r\n- Install tools:\r\n- Others:\r\n",
